{"detail":{"type":"rate_limit_error","code":"concurrent_limit_exceeded","message":"Too many concurrent requests. Your current subscription is associated with a maximum of 4 concurrent requests (running in parallel). This is done such that a single user does not overwhelm our systems and affect other users negatively. Please upgrade your subscription or contact sales if you want to increase this limit.","status":"too_many_concurrent_requests","request_id":"8f44cea1207b30e6aa81aac550e17c21","docs_url":"https://elevenlabs.io/docs/eleven-api/resources/errors#rate-limiting-and-concurrency"}}